<collectingCountry box="[599,666,945,968]" name="Malta" pageId="14" pageNumber="15">Marta</collectingCountry>
in N. 
<collectingCountry box="[742,855,943,967]" name="Colombia" pageId="14" pageNumber="15">Colombia</collectingCountry>
, in the Department of Magdalena. This subspecies flies high up on the forest canopy.
</paragraph>
